# Government Tender Announcement

## Federal Government of Canada
* **Reference**: WS3895212900
* **Title**: CFIA Lockers
* **GUSPC Category**: 56100000 – Accommodation Furniture, 56101520 – Lockers

### Procurement Information

* [NoticeURL](http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/15927239?extsite=MTU5MjcyMzlfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==)
* [Contracting Entity Address](https://maps.google.com/maps?entry=11 Laurier St, Phase III, Place du Portage, Gatineau, Quebec, Canada K1A 0S5)
* **Contracting Entity Contact Information**: LeBlanc, Kristelle (SPAC/PSPC) / Email: [kristelle.leblanc@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca](mailto:kristelle.leblanc@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca)

### Procurement Description

The Department of Public Works and Government Services (PWGSC) invites eligible bidders to submit a Request for Proposal (RFP) for the purchase, delivery, and installation of office furniture, specifically metal filing and storage cabinets to the Canadian Food Inspection Agency (CFIA) in Moncton, New Brunswick, by May 22, 2023. This procurement is set aside under the federal government’s Procurement Strategy for Aboriginal Business and is excluded from international trade agreements under the provision for set-asides for small and minority businesses.

### Eligibility

Only pre-qualified and supply arrangement holders of the PWGSC Supply Arrangement (SA) are eligible to bid.

### Deadline for Submission

The tender closing date is May 26, 2023 at 14:00:00. Only submissions received by the deadline will be accepted.

### Procurement Evaluation Criteria

The procurement evaluation criteria will be based on the lowest price.

The Federal Government of Canada reserves the right to cancel this bid request at any time. Note that there is no postauction.

Revised on [insert revision date] []>(). ERC added text has been preserved to ensure continuity.

### Disclaimer

This offer contains confidential and proprietary information. This offer is limited to the specific contract or purchase order identified. No rights can be derived or assigned to third parties by this agreement.
